response.overview: On September 15th TNT Extreme Wrestling: Project X 2023 is live on FITE+ straight from Hangar 34 in Liverpool, UK. The event features the Ultimate X Match where Robbie X goes against Starboy Charlie against Scotty Rawk against Leon Slater.  Also in the lineup:  GCW Ultraviolent Title Match  Rina Yamashita (c) vs Emersyn Jayne  Tag Team Match  Lykos Gym (Kid Lykos & Kid Lykos II) vs Los Vipers (Arez & Latigo)  Gringo Loco vs Dan Moloney  TNT Women's Title Match  Alexxis Falcon (c) vs Masha Slamovich  TNT Ultra X Title vs Career Match  Nico Angelo (c) vs Man Like DeReiss  Tag Team Match  BUSSY (Allie Katch & Effy) vs Scouse And Proud (Harley Hudson & Lizzy Evo)  TNT World Title Match  Charles Crowley (c) vs Jordan Oliver
response.title: TNT Extreme Wrestling Project X 2023
